beer.beer_description: Hawthorn Pale Ale is our unique interpretation of this classic and popular style. This Pale Ale presents a rich and com-plex malt character, derived from a bold blend of five different types of grain. Lightly kilned, the use of our specialty malts gives this beer a deep golden colour. The malt character is wonderfully balanced by the inclusion of five comple-mentary varieties of hops. Sourced from New Zealand, Southern England and the US Pacific Northwest , these fresh hops deliver a saporous fruit and spice flavour, whilst a generous addition of hops late in the boil presents a delightful floral and citrus aroma
